</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="50">3.2. Setting up shortcuts</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Default shortcuts are saved in this tab. Shortcuts are used for many functions that are carried out on a regular basis. You can use shortcuts to open important menus in plentymarkets or to switch between tabs and tab levels. For example, the shortcut <strong>Alt + I</strong> opens the item overview. <strong>Alt + W</strong> is used to close the tab again.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Learn more about shortcuts in the following video tutorial:</p>
</div>
<div class="videoblock">
<div class="content">
<iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/122105765" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
</div>
</div>
